entor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"e20504f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cfa6032\" data-id=\"cfa6032\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8406635 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8406635\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What can be done to control cockroaches?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42748e1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"42748e1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Brown-banded cockroaches are a common indoor pest found in homes and businesses. These insects are known for their distinctive brown bands on their wings and bodies, and they are often smaller than other species of cockroaches. To control and eradicate brown-banded cockroaches, there are several steps that homeowners or business owners can take.<\/p><ul><li>The first step is eliminating any food sources that may attract the roaches. This includes cleaning up crumbs, spills, and other debris regularly.<\/li><li>Additionally, it&#8217;s important to store food in sealed containers and keep garbage in tightly sealed bags or bins.<\/li><li>Another option is to use bait stations that contain an insecticide designed explicitly for brown-banded cockroaches.<\/li><li>Another effective method for controlling brown-banded cockroach populations is by sealing any cracks or crevices where the insects may enter the building. This includes gaps around windows and doors and holes in walls or floors.<\/li><\/ul><p>In some cases, professional pest control services from ACME Pest Solutions may be necessary if infestations have become severe or if there are multiple entry areas into the building. By taking these measures consistently over time, it&#8217;s possible to keep brown-banded cockroach populations under control and prevent future infestations from occurring altogether.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4b9d9e2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4b9d9e2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3995655\" data-id=\"3995655\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cdf0ae6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"cdf0ae6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"Article\",\r\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\r\n    \"@id\": \"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/brown-banded-cockroaches\/\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"headline\": \"Brown-banded cockroaches\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Brown-banded cockroaches are a common species of cockroach found in many households. These small pests typically range from \u00bd to \u215d inches long, making them easy to miss unless you're actively looking for them. They have a light brown coloration on